Robbie Rogers (LA Galaxy) wins a free kick on the left wing.

timelineItems.name: Jennifer Gonzales
timelineItems.text: Wow. Not cool Boswell. #DCvLA

timelineItems.name: Louis East
timelineItems.text: Mika Vayrynen fires a free-kick just wide. His first start in midfield for the Galaxy tonight #DCvLA

timelineItems.comment: Corner,  LA Galaxy. Conceded by Bobby Boswell.

timelineItems.name: Louis East
timelineItems.text: Just a couple of minutes left. Looks like a goalless draw... #DCvLA

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Nick DeLeon (D.C. United) right footed shot from outside the box is too high following a corner.
Corner,  D.C. United. Conceded by Edson Buddle.

timelineItems.desc: Goal!  D.C. United 1, LA Galaxy 0. Chris Pontius (D.C. United) header from the left side of the six yard box to the bottom left corner. Assisted by Nick DeLeon.
timelineItems.title: GOAL: Chris Pontius heads home a winner at the death

timelineItems.comment: Offside, LA Galaxy. Omar González tries a through ball, but Alan Gordon is caught offside.

timelineItems.name: Charles Boehm
timelineItems.text: #DCU going square or back far too often lately. I'm thinking they've reached the limitations of Olsen's 4-4-2. #DCvLA

timelineItems.name: Adam Serrano
timelineItems.text: #DCU GOAL! All kinds of danger in the penalty area and Chris Pointus comes up on the end of it. Heartbreaker for the #LAGalaxy.

timelineItems.name: regularguy
timelineItems.text: The points are nice but no one should get three points after that #dcu

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, D.C. United 1, LA Galaxy 0.
